---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home | Robotics Portfolio">
	<div class="max-w-3xl py-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6">
			Hi, I'm an MSc Robotics student at <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">TU Delft</span>.
		</h1>
		<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
			Welcome to my portfolio. I specialize in control theory, computer vision, and building intelligent autonomous systems.
			I use this space to showcase my research, projects, and explorations in robotics.
		</p>

		<div class="flex gap-4">
			<a href="/projects" class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
				View Projects
			</a>
			<a href="https://github.com/username" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="px-6 py-3 bg-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-300 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
				GitHub
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-20">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pb-2">Recent Focus</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3 text-blue-500">•</span>
					<span><strong>Advanced Control Systems:</strong> Model Predictive Control (MPC) and Non-linear Dynamics.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3 text-blue-500">•</span>
					<span><strong>Robotic Manipulation:</strong> Kinematics, trajectory planning, and grasping.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="mr-3 text-blue-500">•</span>
					<span><strong>Software Engineering:</strong> ROS2, C++, and Python for robotics applications.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
